\subsection{Environment and URL visibility policy}

The environment toggle applies uniformly across layouts, but the URL toggle is
deliberately narrower: only the QR-less article branches can hide the printed
URL because QR-bearing layouts read that caption from the regenerated sidecar.
The tests pin both the shared precedence rules and that visibility boundary
directly on [[mc()]].

